<div style="text-align: justify">
	<h5>
	The ILLC Diversity Talk is an initiative of the ILLC Diversity Committee. <p> </p> 
	The goal of the ILLC Diversity Talks is to show how research carried out at the ILLC interacts with recent works and findings in the area of diversity, broodly understood. 
	It will be an opportunity for ILLC members to reflect on current research and practices which could foster diversity and inclusion within the institute.
